Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:12.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无法入眠的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:16.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}独自一人叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:19.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大家又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:23.40,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}总觉得很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:29.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}广阔的大地上 一粒种子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:32.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸展开根系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:40.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}又结出青色的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:45.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要早些成为橙色的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沐浴着你的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:52.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}理想和梦想不断膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:55.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快察觉到吧 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:59.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天也品尝了橙子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:02.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}依然酸涩 不禁落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:06.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不能让它像我一样被丢弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:08.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}全部吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:15.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喜欢你哦 要哭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:22.00,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喜欢你哦 喜欢你哦
